rkishny.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.turkishny.com/sport-news/8-sport-news/255966-gokhan-tore-ile-esra-bilgic-evlendi|title=G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re ile Esra Bilgi\u00e7 Evlendi|access-date=2018-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102013325/http://www.turkishny.com/sport-news/8-sport-news/255966-gokhan-tore-ile-esra-bilgic-evlendi|archive-date=2018-01-02|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name=\"div\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnnturk.com/magazin/esra-bilgic-ile-gokhan-tore-bosandi|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 ile G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re bo\u015fand\u0131|publisher=CNN T\u00fcrk|date=17 June 2019|accessdate=17 June 2019}}</ref>\n| children           = \n| website            = \n}}\n<nowiki>{{}}</nowiki>\n\n'''[[Esra Bilgi\u00e7|Esra]] Bilgi\u00e7''' (born 14 October 1992)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haberturk.com/magazin/herkes-bunu-konusuyor/haber/1189311-esra-bilgic-kimdir|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 kimdir?|publisher=}}</ref> is a [[Turkey|Turkish]] actress and model. She portrayed [[Halime Hatun]] in the historical adventure television series ''[[Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul]]'' from 2014 to 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aksam.com.tr/televizyon/dirilis-ertugrul-yeni-74-bolum-fragmani-son-bolum-trt-1de/haber-587343|title=Dirili\u015f Ertu\u011frul 74. yeni b\u00f6l\u00fcm fragman\u0131 TRT 1'de nefes kesti - Ak\u015fam|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mediaturkey.net/turkishdramas/dirilis-ertugrul-trt1-succes|title=Dirilis Ertugrul 's success is approved!|date=December 19, 2014|access-date=January 1, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530224836/http://www.mediaturkey.net/turkishdramas/dirilis-ertugrul-trt1-succes/|archive-date=May 30, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ahaber.com.tr/galeri/yasam/esra-bilgic-ve-gokhan-tore-mutluluga-evet-dedi|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 ve G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re mutlulu\u011fa 'evet' dedi|website=A Haber}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnnturk.com/esra-bilgic|title=esra bilgi\u00e7 ile ilgili haberler|website=CNN T\u00fcrk}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/cinema/2017/03/15/turkish-history-themed-series-dirilis-ertugrul-enjoyed-in-60-countries|title=Turkish history-themed series Dirili\u015f Ertu\u011frul enjoyed in 60 countries|publisher=|accessdate=27 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.trt.net.tr/espanol/cultura-y-arte/2016/12/07/la-trt-fue-premiada-en-varias-categorias-625259|title=La TRT fue premiada en varias categor\u00edas - TRT Espa\u00f1ol|website=www.trt.net.tr}}</ref> She is currently the leading actress in the crime drama series ''Ramo''.\n\n==Career==\n\nFrom 2014, She starred in the TV series ''[[Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul]]'' telecast on [[TRT 1]]. Her co-actors were [[Engin Altan D\u00fczyatan]] and H\u00fclya Darcan. ''Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul'' is about the heroic story of the father of [[Osman I]], [[Ertu\u011frul]], who turns a small tribe of Anatolya into a Sultanate.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haberler.com/dirilis-ertugrul-yilin-en-populer-dizisi-oldu-9130237-haberi/|title=Dirili\u015f 'Ertu\u011frul' Y\u0131l\u0131n En Pop\u00fcler Dizisi Oldu!|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sabah.com.tr/magazin/2017/10/22/esra-bilgic-ve-gokhan-tore-evlendi-iste-dugun-fotograflari|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 ve G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re d\u00fcn evlendi! - \u0130\u015fte d\u00fc\u011f\u00fcn foto\u011fraflar\u0131|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailysabah.com/nation/2014/12/11/turkeys-new-tv-series-about-the-founding-of-the-ottoman-empire-tops-the-ratings |title=Turkey's new TV series about the founding of the Ottoman empire tops the ratings|work= |first= |last= |date=December 12, 2014}}</ref> Esra Bilgi\u00e7 appeared as [[Halime Hatun]] in the series, but in 2018 she left ''Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul'' because of the changes in the new season; her character, however, died in 1281, and not as early as it was shown in the TV series.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sabah.com.tr/magazin/2016/11/02/gokhan-tore-ile-esra-bilgic-gizlice-nisanlandi|title=G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re ile Esra Bilgi\u00e7 gizlice ni\u015fanland\u0131|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haberakar.com/dirilis-ertugrulun-halimesi-esra-bilgic-gokhan-tore-ile-nisanlandi-haberi-15834|title=Dirili\u015f Ertu\u011frul'un Halime'si Esra Bilgi\u00e7 G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re ile ni\u015fanland\u0131|date=2 November 2016|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haberler.com/gokhan-tore-oyuncu-sevgilisi-esra-bilgic-le-8116925-haberi/|title=G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re, Oyuncu Sevgilisi Esra Bilgi\u00e7'le Evleniyor|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aksam.com.tr/magazin/esra-bilgic-ile-gokhan-tore-evleniyor/haber-485757|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 ile G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re evleniyor - Ak\u015fam|publisher=}}</ref>\nEsra also appeared in ''Bir Umut Yeter''. In 2019, Bilgi\u00e7 was asked to play a leading role in the film ''Adani\u015f Kutsal Kavga''. The film will be released in March, 2020. She is currently the female lead in the Turkish crime-drama TV series ''Ramo'', which co-stars [[Murat_Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m_(actor)|Murat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m]].{{cn|date=January 2020}}\n\n==Personal life==\nEsra Bilgi\u00e7 began dating a professional Turkish footballer, [[G\u00f6khan T\u00f6re]], in 2014. The couple got married on 21 October 2017 and divorced on 17 June 2019. <ref name=\"div\"/> She studied the subject of \"International Relations\" at Bilkent International University, Istanbul,<ref name=\"turkishny.com\"/> and is currently studying law at \u0130stanbul \u015eehir University.<ref>{{cite web|title=Esra Bilgi\u00e7 - Twitter|publisher=|url=https://twitter.com/esbilgic/status/1209535240420700161}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:LightSteelBlue\"|TV Series\n|-\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Year\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Title\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Role\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Note \n|-\n|2014\u20132018\n|''[[Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul]]''\n|[[Halime Hatun]]\n|Main role\n|-\n|2018\n|''Bir Umut Yeter''\n|Derya Akar\n|Main role\n|-\n|2020\n|''Ramo''\n|Sibel Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m\n|Main role\n|} \n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:LightSteelBlue\"|Films\n|-\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Year\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Title\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Role\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Note \n|-\n|2020\n|''Adani\u015f Kutsal Kavga''\n| Cemre\n|Main role\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{refimprove section|date=November 2019}}\nBilgi\u00e7 has won several awards. Some of them are: \n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! colspan=5 style=\"background:LightSteelBlue\"| Awards\n|-\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Year\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Awards Ceremony\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Category\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Project\n!style=\"background:#CCCCCC\"| Result\n|-\n| 2014\n| Antalya TV Awards\n| Best Female Actress in series\n| rowspan=8| [[Dirili\u015f: Ertu\u011frul]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n|2015\n| Sosyal Fark\u0131ndal\u0131k \u00d6d\u00fclleri \n|Best Female Actress in series\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n| 2015\n| Sadri Al\u0131\u015f\u0131k \u00d6d\u00fclleri|18. Sadri Al\u0131\u015f\u0131k Theater and cinema Awards\n| Best Female Actress\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n|2015\n| Anadolu Media \u00d6d\u00fclleri \n| Best Actress of the Series \n| {{Won}}\n|-\n|2016\n| T\u00fcrkiye Gen\u00e7lik \u00d6d\u00fclleri\n| Best Female Actress\n| {{Won}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|7061820|Esra Bilgi\u00e7}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bilgi\u00e7, Esra}}\n\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Catego