 <ref>\u4ee5\u4e0b\u3001[http://www.pref.kanagawa.jp/uploaded/attachment/455244.pdf \u300c\u8b70\u4f1a\u306e\u6982\u8981\u30002012\u300d]{{Dead link|date=February 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\uff08\u795e\u5948\u5ddd\u770c\u8b70\u4f1a\uff09\u3092\u53c2\u7167\u3002{{dead link|date=March 2020}}</ref>. In the first assembly 47 members were elected by registered votes from one district and 15 counties<ref>1\u533a15\u90e1\u3068\u306f\u3001[[\u6a2a\u6d5c\u533a]]\u3068\u3001[[\u4e45\u826f\u5c90\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u6a58\u6a39\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u90fd\u7b51\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u897f\u591a\u6469\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u5357\u591a\u6469\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u5317\u591a\u6469\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u4e09\u6d66\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u938c\u5009\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u9ad8\u5ea7\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u8db3\u67c4\u4e0a\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u8db3\u67c4\u4e0b\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u5927\u4f4f\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u6dd8\u7dbe\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u611b\u7532\u90e1]]\u3001[[\u6d25\u4e45\u4e95\u90e1]]\u306e15\u90e1\u3002</ref>. The term is of 4 years.\n\n==Organisation==\n===President and Vice-President===\n\n*'''President''': Makoto Kunimatsu ([[Liberal Democratic Party (Japan)|LDP]]), elected from Fujisawa \n*'''Vice-President''': Takanori Takita ([[Constitutional Democratic Party|CDP]]), elected from Nakahara-ku.\n\n==Reference==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Prefectural assemblies of Japan}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Prefectural assemblies of Japan]]\n[[Category:Politics of Kanagawa Prefecture]]\n", "name_user": "HeirofRaider", "label": "safe", "comment": "Constitutional Democratic Party of Japan added, Russian Constitutional Democratic Party subtracted.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanagawa_Prefectural_Assembly"}
